Did I ever tell you about the time I found Henry Kissinger's shapewear in an abandoned storage unit just inside the national radio quiet zone? What a trip, let me tell you. We were somewhere near the Virginia State line in the Blue Ridge mountains, close enough to see decommissioned radio telescopes. 
